{"tid":2318216,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"會計師公會民主改革派大勝選舉","createTime":"2020-12-09T07:16:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T12:27:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"25ffba5b990062363638941d2fbd4fb6f4ee2663","tid":2318216,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T07:16:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201209/2TO5FYYO4ZAUNDT77KYR3USQI4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201209%2F2TO5FYYO4ZAUNDT77KYR3USQI4%2F&d=zhjqHwqbwmwTWRz%2FWGYaULHzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=0ad61376\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201209%2F2TO5FYYO4ZAUNDT77KYR3USQI4%2F&h=c34b2190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201209/2TO5FYYO4ZAUNDT77KYR3USQI4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n會計師公會民主改革派大勝選舉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/D8SRGQEX8dXLUMQdPfazm9qSdlM=/957x538/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EWRP3YCVXVG4FOE6JNJ5E4WCRA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FD8SRGQEX8dXLUMQdPfazm9qSdlM%3D%2F957x538%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEWRP3YCVXVG4FOE6JNJ5E4WCRA.jpg&h=388b4356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■香港會計師公會理事選舉中當選的民主、改革派包括鄭中正等。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港會計師公會（HKICPA）理事選舉投票結果出爐，民主派及改革派奪下五席，大獲全勝。新一任會長及副會長將在星期四（10日）舉行的理事大會有結果。<br />\n<br />\n根據消息人士透露，今次投票人數逾一萬人。當選民主、改革派理事包括陳維漢、鄭中正、區紀倫、鄭皓朗、王榮熙；建制派則有林智遠及方蘊萱。<br />\n<br />\n香港會計師公會於1973年成立，至今有47年歷史，為香港唯一法定會計師註冊組織，目前會員超過4.6萬人，均為認可（certified）會計師。現時，會計師公會有 21個常設席位，每名理事任期為兩年，其中由政府委任4席、政府官員出任2席，至於上屆會長則佔1席，其餘14席則分兩年輪替以選舉產生，即每年選出7個席位。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或可推動一人一票選會長<br />\n<br />\n於去年的理事選舉之中，民主及改革派大勝取下6席，加上今年理事選舉取得5席，意味着民主及改革派取得11席，佔21席逾半，似乎可推動會計界一人一票選會長。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，公會早前。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"30b478f281cb095bd3b80938e1886b31b3e45849","tid":2318216,"uid":386729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T12:27:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2319966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2319966</a><br />\n會計師公會有新會長啦！"}]}